# Tests And Validation

- Use focused tests while iterating, then run `npm run agent:check` before claiming completion.
- Prefer pure helper tests for scheduling, template, form, and readiness behavior over brittle full-page snapshots.
- Add repository tests with schema or SQL changes.
- Add send-safety tests when changing campaigns, deliveries, scheduler, mailer, direct email, communications, or email test mode.
- Keep agent assets discoverable and covered by `tests/agent-assets.test.ts`.
- If validation cannot be run, state exactly which command was skipped and why.
